Subject: Re: [T2] RE: 71 Rear Brake Shoes

Production for the 1971 model year was from August 1970 to July 1971.  August 1971 started the 1972 production year.  The shoes they have should be correct for your 1971 unless someone has changed something during the last 36+ years.

Hope this helps.

Brad Spear
'72 Westfalia (6 June 1972 production date)
Burnsville, MN

